Miscellaneous Highlights: The Kansas City Royals beat the Washington Nationals with a final score of 84-69, improving their record to 39-38 away and 84-74 overall. The Nationals' record remains at 36-41 home and 69-89 overall.
Others: The game was held at Nationals Park in Washington, District of Columbia, with an attendance of 16,670 and a game time of 2:24.
